{"tid":1597434,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［求神回覆］被藍絲惡意投訴 要寫解釋信","createTime":"2019-09-27T02:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:00:15.000Z","uid":92713,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfce91b166a2ac18c05bc9dcb409a5fc8b34e74","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n咁大家都知康文署泳池一向會升國旗區旗<br />\n咁小弟有日如常去開工 當緊更嘅時候<br />\n就有個呀叔走埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀叔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂你呢度支國旗低過支區旗喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（望一望支旗）哦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你整返佢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦<br />\n（支旗嘅示意圖）其實真係低咗少少嘅 但竟然有人會去留意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VQLvEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VQLvEC.jpg&h=d792ed24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呀叔就行開咗 可能見我無即時去整<br />\n極速走去同清潔姐姐講<br />\n咁清潔姐姐見俾客屌，好快都fix返<br />\n<br />\n然後點知今日收到office通知<br />\n原來個呀叔走去打1823投訴我<br />\n話我唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開咗file要我寫解釋信<br />\n<br />\n第一，當時我係當緊更（巡兩米主池）<br />\n我睇緊個池，做救生員最大責任都係睇住啲人唔好浸親啫<br />\n我梗係唔會即時就突然行開走去幫個呀叔跟進，<br />\n我都要等休息時間先去同office講<br />\n（因為我呢啲小員工，清潔姐姐通常要office落order先點得郁佢地做嘢）<br />\n<br />\n第二，升旗唔係我地救生員升，清潔升㗎，關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n升得唔好都唔係我責任掛，明明係清潔做嘢嗱西<br />\n點解office要我寫解釋信，我究竟有咩責任要負<br />\n我有應佢機，唔係唔理佢，只係唔係即時處理咁解<br />\n升返支旗唔會urgent到緊要得過睇住個池呀？<br />\n<br />\n家陣盡忠職守都要俾人搞，個呀叔真係好無聊<br />\nOffice又要渣正嚟做，因為投訴對象係我<br />\n小弟表示無言同無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求連登巴絲指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點樣寫呢封垃圾解釋信<br />\n事關小弟文筆唔好，驚講多錯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果俾office寫花個file就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568541ddff8713b2d801e25f7ad38a0982060fc2","tid":1597434,"uid":219583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"寫?寫閪咩寫 比D尊嚴啦唔撚該"},{"pid":"3c0d7d6cac3650a74a248f513b601e8af2cb0b18","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"568541ddff8713b2d801e25f7ad38a0982060fc2","tid":1597434,"uid":219583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"寫?寫閪咩寫 比D尊嚴啦唔撚該"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"我諗住唔識寫就一直唔撚寫 拖到完季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過驚office追 緊咬不放要我寫"},{"pid":"4443fdd93203c11c6d44289a249a11e495877b3e","tid":1597434,"uid":219583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"追囉 最多未唔撚撈政府 搵私家救生仲好啦"},{"pid":"fad068e001b9e395abea516ba72863f94c742851","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4443fdd93203c11c6d44289a249a11e495877b3e","tid":1597434,"uid":219583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"追囉 最多未唔撚撈政府 搵私家救生仲好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔太適合返私池 不過多謝建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7ed908eac6005bf2d9ad2676da2645b3591094","tid":1597434,"uid":280457,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:51:18.000Z","msg":"咪話當時已收到投訴人的要求，但因為履行救生員保障泳池生命安全職責，所以稍後才能通知負責升旗的的清潔同事跟進<br />\n然後咪如果造成不便之處敬請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">體</span>諒"},{"pid":"eea18ec98148cfec0193d1bb1f152d96f763998c","tid":1597434,"uid":134620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />N9 OFFICE/ON99 1823<br />\n                                就X月X日有泳客投訴之解釋信<br />\n<br />\n事件發生說明:<br />\n&quot;同啊叔既原整對話&quot;+ 清潔姐姐得悉事件後好快都fix返<br />\n<br />\n應對方式:<br />\n我睇緊個池,想休息時間先去同office講<br />\n（因為我呢啲小員工，清潔姐姐通常要office落order先點得郁佢地做嘢）<br />\n但姐姐係我行動前就處理左<br />\n<br />\n個人對事件看法:<br />\n第一，當時我係當緊更（巡兩米主池）<br />\n我睇緊個池，做救生員最大責任都係睇住啲人唔好浸親啫<br />\n我梗係唔會即時就突然行開走去幫個呀叔跟進，<br />\n<br />\n第二，升旗唔係我地救生員升，清潔升㗎，關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n升得唔好都唔係我責任掛，明明係清潔做嘢嗱西<br />\n點解office要我寫解釋信，我究竟有咩責任要負<br />\n我有應佢機，唔係唔理佢，只係唔係即時處理咁解<br />\n升返支旗唔會urgent到緊要得過睇住個池呀？"},{"pid":"1626ff71dd7356c55c6e1defd2dd7f2287e9b6f4","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁都要解釋？邊個叫你解釋 康文經理？"},{"pid":"2f4c4004cf51b4fe83b2fd214cdda9caa5c4bc93","tid":1597434,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"咁下次搵人扮浸親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90b7b8bf80467f2f38363848f2e2a4131584c80","tid":1597434,"uid":169079,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"電光火石之間未能分辦"},{"pid":"a0a2e79d90e576b28a909bec74a43d89db5f883b","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1626ff71dd7356c55c6e1defd2dd7f2287e9b6f4","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁都要解釋？邊個叫你解釋 康文經理？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知 佢其實想我點解釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOffice都係一層層咁叫落嚟<br />\nA3搵高技搵我咁囉 我諗經理都知掛"},{"pid":"f8dcf6a0ffe3e86e6228f66e563067f09fe0580a","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d90b7b8bf80467f2f38363848f2e2a4131584c80","tid":1597434,"uid":169079,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"re