ces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點樣寫呢封垃圾解釋信<br />\n事關小弟文筆唔好，驚講多錯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果俾office寫花個file就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"其實有乜好解釋，升旗又唔係你負責，投訴就搵番負責嗰個啦，我係要救人"},{"pid":"5b42c1aef0166ff072a1a1c6cab8a677ceb15ad5","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f4c4004cf51b4fe83b2fd214cdda9caa5c4bc93","tid":1597434,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"咁下次搵人扮浸親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"下次有客一行埋嚟搵我講嘢就直接跳落水算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔撚聽 我唔撚知 我唔撚理"},{"pid":"28b570b7da5350f6c1042852ad07d522d42b2af8","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d00c8deb935d94e89e3b86d243a5862b9d268b6","tid":1597434,"uid":300589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ddfce91b166a2ac18c05bc9dcb409a5fc8b34e74","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n咁大家都知康文署泳池一向會升國旗區旗<br />\n咁小弟有日如常去開工 當緊更嘅時候<br />\n就有個呀叔走埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀叔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂你呢度支國旗低過支區旗喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（望一望支旗）哦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你整返佢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦<br />\n（支旗嘅示意圖）其實真係低咗少少嘅 但竟然有人會去留意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VQLvEC.jpg\" data-t