19-09-27T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"但唔可以咁寫架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b45880fd36906b856d854a996baf9a5a0e14fa7","tid":1597434,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8dcf6a0ffe3e86e6228f66e563067f09fe0580a","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d90b7b8bf80467f2f38363848f2e2a4131584c80","tid":1597434,"uid":169079,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"電光火石之間未能分辦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"電光火石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有創意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"佢屌都唔係要你解釋嫁啦，是但寫d野射走佢咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112957865453a43e7e97c905767143f4b646cc5a","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eea18ec98148cfec0193d1bb1f152d96f763998c","tid":1597434,"uid":134620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />N9 OFFICE/ON99 1823<br />\n                                就X月X日有泳客投訴之解釋信<br />\n<br />\n事件發生說明:<br />\n&quot;同啊叔既原整對話&quot;+ 清潔姐姐得悉事件後好快都fix返<br />\n<br />\n應對方式:<br />\n我睇緊個池,想休息時間先去同office講<br />\n（因為我呢啲小員工，清潔姐姐通常要office落order先點得郁佢地做嘢）<br />\n但姐姐係我行動前就處理左<br />\n<br />\n個人對事件看法:<br />\n第一，當時我係當緊更（巡兩米主池）<br />\n我睇緊個池，做救生員最大責任都係睇住啲人唔好浸親啫<br />\n我梗係唔會即時就突然行開走去幫個呀叔跟進，<br />\n<br />\n第二，升旗唔係我地救生員升，清潔升㗎，關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n升得唔好都唔係我責任掛，明明係清潔做嘢嗱西<br />\n點解office要我寫解釋信，我究竟有咩責任要負<br />\n我有應佢機，唔係唔理佢，只係唔係即時處理咁解<br />\n升返支旗唔會urgent到緊要得過睇住個池呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"直接print呢個post出嚟 一嘢扔落經理塊面算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11675df35ad122cfe2d017d5cd0429fc9a126b8d","tid":1597434,"uid":22173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"參考下BINGO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccKng0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccKng0.png&h=0198c08b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae7ef76644af21904305fa78b902210eba4b23c3","tid":1597434,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"大風咋"},{"pid":"97c0d39a064d4fb79c749ce27b6c6241eee76ebd","tid":1597434,"uid":164851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"其實你已經打晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16543f1ae0b567f86ee801f47a4c389e3e1fda46","tid":1597434,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"錯覺黎"},{"pid":"99c378675c526aaa2fc42966d9934c5fdc9d82b8","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11675df35ad122cfe2d017d5cd0429fc9a126b8d","tid":1597434,"uid":22173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"參考下BINGO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccKng0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccKng0.png&h=0198c08b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"支國旗十分克制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e225ee0363f81fcefa117220ae26779b6344ea9","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97c0d39a064d4fb79c749ce27b6c6241eee76ebd","tid":1597434,"uid":164851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"其實你已經打晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"我真心覺得自己無做錯嘅<br />\n不過組織唔到點寫好佢 好好睇睇咁伸冤"},{"pid":"3908741288007e5f4dcd7cbf8d9f6669e35777a5","tid":1597434,"uid":184597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得你最有理有據既地方就係：<br />\n<br />\n首先，升旗並非你既職責，但當時因爲有市民所求，所以你都禮貌上回應左佢-「當你處理好手頭上既工作之後，會盡快處理。」 而你未處理好你手頭上既工作時，市民就已經責怪你冇即時處理，咁樣係對你不公。而事實上，支旗後尾亦處好左，以證明左你係冇「膚顯」佢。"},{"pid":"adb3082f3ec7b430d2360bc1096c1460681a682c","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3908741288007e5f4dcd7cbf8d9f6669e35777a5","tid":1597434,"uid":184597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:38:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得你最有理有據既地方就係：<br />\n<br />\n首先，升旗並非你既職責，但當時因爲有市民所求，所以你都禮貌上回應左佢-「當你處理好手頭上既工作之後，會盡快處理。」 而你未處理好你手頭上既工作時，市民就已經責怪你冇即時處理，咁樣係對你不公。而事實上，支旗後尾亦處好左，以證明左你係冇「膚顯」佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係不公<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講得好<br />\ntw敷衍 正字"},{"pid":"1d19568b7a53246b88439671cfea526808c46334","tid":1597434,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=4f80727a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=76f3521f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch404gk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh404gk.jpg&h=d7485b64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HcRruH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HcRruH.jpg&h=e7517ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SkSVn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SkSVn3.jpg&h=a53c058c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMqC6uK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMqC6uK.jpg&h=7e56ff57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPbF4gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPbF4gq.jpg&h=40897d98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13aabc951c23eb82b2259794388012265892d4a8","tid":1597434,"uid":164932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"季節性？ 季節性就咪撚理鳩佢啦 咁等人用 吹得你脹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36f21c3e9156f3580867f3cc603d425ad12d160","tid":1597434,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"認唔認得阿叔<br />\n下次見到佢當面同佢道歉然後影張合照大和解再放上黎"},{"pid":"945833b862a1056f88b41805e9e9ee8599d82b9e","tid":1597434,"uid":312150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"11675df35ad122cfe2d017d5cd0429fc9a126b8d","tid":1597434,"uid":22173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"參考下BINGO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccKng0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccKng0.png&h=0198c08b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"本人一如以往，緊守崗位，服務市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce42d63c9a5c1f13b3f61770384ca4ae7abdb1e6","tid":1597434,"uid":152108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11675df35ad122cfe2d017d5cd0429fc9a126b8d","tid":1597434,"uid":22173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"參考下BINGO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccKng0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccKng0.png&h=0198c08b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"全部都可以用落封解釋信度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5411a0380a7770cc08f9401dfb8ab05b4052df8e","tid":1597434,"uid":267909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a2e79d90e576b28a909bec74a43d89db5f883b","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1626ff71dd7356c55c6e1defd2dd7f2287e9b6f4","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁都要解釋？邊個叫你解釋 康文經理？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知 佢其實想我點解釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOffice都係一層層咁叫落嚟<br />\nA3搵高技搵我咁囉 我諗經理都知掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"最緊要寫你本身責任係睇住個池<br />\n當時已即時應機<br />\n但不可以係睇池晚時間走開<br />\n只可係休息或見到清潔亞姐時同佢講<br />\n<br />\n最後要重申多次本身職責及安全為先"},{"pid":"11981e55d40d63f1904d21e915a3f29f35b51af4","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13aabc951c23eb82b2259794388012265892d4a8","tid":1597434,"uid":164932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"季節性？ 季節性就咪撚理鳩佢啦 咁等人用 吹得你脹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"順手吐個苦水先<br />\n時薪都串過季節性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼話射波就射波<br />\n做時薪 無期望就無失望<br />\n季節性好多制肘 做又做得多 假又唔俾人放<br />\n即係逼人sick leave囉 揀邊日放假都成日話唔得<br />\n咁唔通唔使做私人嘢咩 假又唔放喇喎<br />\nOT做做埋埋儲落啲鐘又多到放唔哂<br />\n最後臨完季先焗住封池嚟俾人放埋啲補鐘同補假<br />\n所以唔好成日問點解無救生員返工所以封池<br />\n係office逼成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d97e4e06966afc046232706f603fb9042e1819","tid":1597434,"uid":34508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0d7d6cac3650a74a248f513b601e8af2cb0b18","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"568541ddff8713b2d801e25f7ad38a0982060fc2","tid":1597434,"uid":219583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"寫?寫閪咩寫 比D尊嚴啦唔撚該"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"我諗住唔識寫就一直唔撚寫 拖到完季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過驚office追 緊咬不放要我寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"寫<br />\n關我撚事 我負責救人唔係整旗"},{"pid":"c4693d7da425c5dde918f14cb24eff37e09c6e41","tid":1597434,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddfce91b166a2ac18c05bc9dcb409a5fc8b34e74","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n咁大家都知康文署泳池一向會升國旗區旗<br />\n咁小弟有日如常去開工 當緊更嘅時候<br />\n就有個呀叔走埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀叔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂你呢度支國旗低過支區旗喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（望一望支旗）哦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁你整返佢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦<br />\n（支旗嘅示意圖）其實真係低咗少少嘅 但竟然有人會去留意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VQLvEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VQLvEC.jpg&h=d792ed24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呀叔就行開咗 可能見我無即時去整<br />\n極速走去同清潔姐姐講<br />\n咁清潔姐姐見俾客屌，好快都fix返<br />\n<br />\n然後點知今日收到office通知<br />\n原來個呀叔走去打1823投訴我<br />\n話我唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開咗file要我寫解釋信<br />\n<br />\n第一，當時我係當緊更（巡兩米主池）<br />\n我睇緊個池，做救生員最大責任都係睇住啲人唔好浸親啫<br />\n我梗係唔會即時就突然行開走去幫個呀叔跟進，<br />\n我都要等休息時間先去同office講<br />\n（因為我呢啲小員工，清潔姐姐通常要office落order先點得郁佢地做嘢）<br />\n<br />\n第二，升旗唔係我地救生員升，清潔升㗎，關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n升得唔好都唔係我責任掛，明明係清潔做嘢嗱西<br />\n點解office要我寫解釋信，我究竟有咩責任要負<br />\n我有應佢機，唔係唔理佢，只係唔係即時處理咁解<br />\n升返支旗唔會urgent到緊要得過睇住個池呀？<br />\n<br />\n家陣盡忠職守都要俾人搞，個呀叔真係好無聊<br />\nOffice又要渣正嚟做，因為投訴對象係我<br />\n小弟表示無言同無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求連登巴絲指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點樣寫呢封垃圾解釋信<br />\n事關小弟文筆唔好，驚講多錯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果俾office寫花個file就唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"宜家已經極唔夠救生員<br />\n佢夠膽炒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"c97e456b38ccdebe047b3cfeb257584ca1f6d4a1","tid":1597434,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"156d2430695c5d9395182ae137f5492b11fb6f7f","tid":1597434,"uid":223006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"與投訴人就高度的定義未能取得一致的共識, 或因角度問題, 不曾發現區旗當時是置於高於國旗的位置, 故本人特此向投訴人鄭重表示...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁關你撚事?!"},{"pid":"cf83cabfad94bfe0f4ee6ce4daa161dbc6fd90bb","tid":1597434,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"你自己都答左當緊更+唔係你職責+都有人處理左<br />\n叫你解釋都係例行工事者"},{"pid":"96c8f3d637cf3547d929045c4a6f86dc2175e30b","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0a2e79d90e576b28a909bec74a43d89db5f883b","tid":1597434,"uid":92713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1626ff71dd7356c55c6e1defd2dd7f2287e9b6f4","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁都要解釋？邊個叫你解釋 康文經理？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知 佢其實想我點解釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOffice都係一層層咁叫落嚟<br />\nA3搵高技搵我咁囉 我諗經理都知掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"邊個叫你解釋 咪問返佢搞支旗時浸死人喺咪佢負責"},{"pid":"da881467fe0fce263a9c233340bd1138cdbb201a","tid":1597434,"uid":245170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"做法不完善，可接受"},{"pid":"4a455a2c4d7cbb617a0ec2c1d41291e27bf707c2","tid":1597434,"uid":19217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"945833b862a1056f88b41805e9e9ee8599d82b9e","tid":1597434,"uid":312150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"11675df35ad122cfe2d017d5cd0429fc9a126b8d","tid":1597434,"uid":22173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"參考下BINGO紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WccKng0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWccKng0.png&h=0198c08b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"本人一如以往，緊守崗位，服務市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c